text: Saadeddine Othmani (; born 16 January 1956) is a Moroccan politician. He was the Prime Minister of Morocco from 2017 until 2021. On 17 March 2017, Saadeddine Othmani was appointed as Prime Minister by King Mohammed VI. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Morocco
